{"id":554750,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/03/【弄个大新闻】习近平梁家河参加劳动照片/","date":"2017-03-24T02:53:19Z","modified":"2017-03-24T07:12:44Z","title":"【弄个大新闻】习近平梁家河“参加劳动”照片——是假的","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>近日，中共党媒对习近平的知青经历进行了又一轮的正面宣传。有网民在微信曝光，称一张被广泛用在颂习视频和宣传资料中的一张照片内，所谓“参加劳动”者并非习本人，而是一位名叫庞沄的知青。庞沄原照曾刊登在《<a href=\"https://books.google.com/books/about/%E5%AE%88%E6%9C%9B%E8%AE%B0%E5%BF%86_%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%9F%A5%E9%9D%92%E6%B0%91%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E6%96%87.html?id=I6NwAAAAIAAJ\" target=\"_blank\">守望记忆——中国知青民间备忘文本</a>》一书中，照片旁的注释赫然写着“庞沄在用柴油机泵水浇地”。</p>\n<p>经数字时代编辑检索发现，《人民日报》微视频《人民代表习近平》、央视微视频《初心·梁家河篇》、近期各种宣传通稿、以及梁家河村史馆的习近平相关资料中均使用了这张乌龙照片。<strong>梁家河村史馆甚至将乌龙照片作为“习近平领着村里人打了梁家河的第一口吃水井”的证据，并称拍照人为习近平弟弟习远平。</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读</strong>：<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170324/19968095\" target=\"_blank\">苹果日报｜陕西务农宣传相片被揭造假 官媒盗用他人旧照为习近平造神</a></p></blockquote>\n<div id=\"attachment_554756\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0644.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-554756\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0644.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0644.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0644-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0644-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">《守望记忆》中的庞沄原照；微信图片</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_554757\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0645.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-554757\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0645.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0645.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0645-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微信图片</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_554770\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/守望记忆.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-554770\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/守望记忆.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"634\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/守望记忆.jpg 944w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/守望记忆-213x300.jpg 213w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/守望记忆-768x1082.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/守望记忆-727x1024.jpg 727w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">《守望记忆》扫描版 第212页截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_554758\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0646.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-554758\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0646.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0646.jpg 450w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0646-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微信图片</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_554759\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0647.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-554759\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0647.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0647.jpg 1280w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0647-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0647-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/IMG_0647-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微信图片</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_554760\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/初心梁家河篇.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-554760\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/初心梁家河篇.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"424\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/初心梁家河篇.jpg 1326w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/初心梁家河篇-300x243.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/初心梁家河篇-768x621.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/初心梁家河篇-1024x828.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">央视《初心·梁家河篇》截图</span></p></div>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309404004701896089839\" target=\"_blank\">西安陈胜｜习近平的“钥匙”与梁家河的“锁”</a></strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/950f8b5djw1f6hirmdtv3j21kw23ub29.jpeg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-554766\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/950f8b5djw1f6hirmdtv3j21kw23ub29.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/950f8b5djw1f6hirmdtv3j21kw23ub29.jpeg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/950f8b5djw1f6hirmdtv3j21kw23ub29-225x300.jpeg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/950f8b5djw1f6hirmdtv3j21kw23ub29-768x1024.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>在梁家河村史馆的诸多珍贵史料中，有一张照片给人留下了深刻的印象。一片土堆下，简陋摆放的柴油机旁，一个看似十多岁、稚气未脱、身体单薄的男孩子正手压拖柄准备抽水淤地。男孩子穿着背心单裤、脚上一双胶鞋已沾满了淤泥。据讲解员介绍，照片拍摄的时间大概在冬春农闲季节，拍摄这张照片的人比照片上的男孩子还年轻几岁，他们是一对兄弟，<strong>其中照片上的主角叫习近平，给他拍照的是从北京前来探望他的弟弟习远平。</strong></p>\n<p>地处延川县的梁家河村山壑丛生，并不富裕，几十年前，连吃水都是问题。1973年，习近平领着村里人打了梁家河的第一口吃水井，而如今，这口井里的水已可以直接引入村民家中。</p></blockquote>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[13222,23589,25917,26276]}